0:11:54.397,000 --> 0:11:56,000
So, what is the secret of our success?

273
0:11:56.609,000 --> 0:11:57,000
Where do we come up with these ideas?

274
0:11:58.45,000 --> 0:11:59,000
How do we develop these kinds of ideas?

275
0:12:00.367,000 --> 0:12:01,000
We have a fully autonomous vehicle

276
0:12:02.181,000 --> 0:12:03,000
that can drive into urban environments.

277
