0:15:48.774,000 --> 0:15:51,000
not because I tell them to, but because we are having too much fun.

365
0:15:52.007,000 --> 0:15:53,000
Which leads to the last topic:

366
0:15:53.685,000 --> 0:15:54,000
do not forget to have fun.

367
0:15:55.578,000 --> 0:15:58,000
That's really the secret of our success, we're having too much fun.

368
0:15:58.815,000 --> 0:16:01,000
I truly believe that highest productivity comes when you're having fun,

369
0:16:02.305,000 --> 0:16:03,000
and that's what we're doing.

370
0:16:03.685,000 --> 0:16:04,000
And there you go.

